data.description: This conveniently located home, near I64, LAFB, NASA and Buckroe Beach, has newer cabinets, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, updated bathrooms and some newer flooring. The sunroom is ideal for family/friend gatherings with easy access to the fenced backyard.  The security system is included.  VA Assumption offered for qualified veterans and active duty at 3% for approximately $235,000 and substitute of entitlement.
